    Scope and Contents
SANGAMON RIVER PROJECT 
Bertha Craig discusses life along the Sangamon River at Petersburg, Illinois: the floods of 1926 and 1943, fishing and swimming, plants and animals along the river, Lake Springfield, Lake Petersburg and its dam, farmer's dams, and home remedies.1 tape, 60 mins., 19 pp.
Interview by Judith Haynes, 1980 
